‌Chapter 6 - The Irrational Rationalist‌ form, that's what religions say. They say, "God is hidden and is getting more and more expressed."
Man is yet the highest expression of that intelligence. The tree is a lower expression; the rock a still lower expression. But all are expressions of the same intelligence. Man, as far as we know on this earth, is the highest expression of that intelligence.
